data.description: We are seeking a motivated and detail-oriented Product Management Intern to join our Americas Region Product Management and Strategy team. In this role, you will collaborate with experienced product managers to support the development and execution of product strategies. You will gain hands-on experience in product management practices and methodologies while working on projects that drive the growth and success of our products. This is an exciting opportunity to develop your product management skills and gain valuable insights into real-world product development and market strategies.
